</ul></nav></div></header><div class="site-inner"><div class="wrap"><div class="content-sidebar-wrap"><main class="content"><article class="post-3795 page type-page status-publish entry" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/CreativeWork"><header class="entry-header"><h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">C&#038;ENjobs Recruitment Advertising</h1> 
</header><div class="entry-content" itemprop="text"><div class="module module-call_to_action"><div class="wrap"><div class="module-inner"><style>.cta-1 {color: #333333;text-align: left;} .cta-1 .cta-heading, .cta-1 .cta-text {color:#333333;} .cta-1 .cta {border-color:#a51e22;color:#a51e22;}</style><div class="call-to-action cta-1"><div class="cta-text"><p><strong><span style="text-align: left; font-size: 26px; color: #a51e22;">C&amp;ENjobs Recruitment Advertising</span></strong></p>
<p><em>C&amp;ENjobs offers the largest pre-vetted talent pool in the world with the exclusive access to the American Chemical Society membership and C&amp;EN readers. We supply you with not only the talent, but also the tools to reach out and make quality connections, allowing you to meet your hiring objectives</em>.</p>
<p>How can you take advantage of C&amp;ENjobs advertising? In C&amp;EN Magazine, there are three types of recruitment ads available in the issues, available both in print, and in its digital edition: Line Ads, Display Ads, and Academic Display Ads. The C&amp;ENjobs online job portal also allows you to post your job listings in 30-day or 60-day ads, plus access the resume database.</p>
<p><strong>Contact Kimberly Mallory, Account Executive for Recruitment Sales &amp; Marketing</strong> (<a href="mailto:k_mallory@acs.org">k_mallory@acs.org</a> or 202-452-8918) or your <a href="http://acsmediakit.org/contact/">international C&amp;EN sales representative</a> for pricing and assistance completing your order.</p>
<p><strong>Need instructions for placing your ads or more details? Please find instructions below. </strong></p>
<ol>
<li>For posting to C&amp;ENjobs online portal ONLY, <a href="http://images.acspubs.org/Web/AmericanChemicalSociety/{529789b9-f458-4098-ac7a-613b163f8132}_HowToPlaceJobBoard.pdf" target="_blank">click here.</a></li>
<li>For advertising in the print and digital editions of C&amp;EN Magazine, <a href="http://images.acspubs.org/Web/AmericanChemicalSociety/{1c2b609e-ce78-4eac-b94c-7834a8796b13}_HowToPlaceCENMag.pdf" target="_blank">click here.</a></li>
<li>BEST PURCHASE: For a dual posting on both C&amp;ENjobs and in the C&amp;EN Magazine, <a href="http://images.acspubs.org/Web/AmericanChemicalSociety/{0901293f-3e2d-4147-99da-4258843fbbd1}_HowToPlaceCENMagAdOnline.pdf" target="_blank">click here. </a>Employers who choose this option are eligible for discounts!</li>
</ol>
<p>To review the C&amp;ENjobs portal, visit <a href="http://chemistryjobs.acs.org/employers/">chemistryjobs.acs.org/employers</a>, and for past issues of C&amp;EN, <a href="http://cen.acs.org/magazine.html" target="_blank">click here</a>.</p>
<p><em>Orders are due by the ad close date. Ad close dates are by noon EST Tuesday 13 calendar days prior to the issue date, excluding legal holidays.</em></p>
